{
  "stem": "11964.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And very frankly, it sustained me quite well at this period to have earned a little extra money for the tutoring.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, one tutorial job paid me in goods, in food.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I would bring some to my younger sister, to the convent, and share some with my older sister.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Anyway, we [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] we got through that period on, on, on, on the back of an awful lot of imagination, a lot of imagination.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had some episodes that were hair-raising.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We knew that some people looked at us in a-- in a-- in a very suspicious way.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We would have to leave from one trolley to another because we didn't like some looks directed at us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we knew that we had to avoid, any way we could, being recognized and being informed upon.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But the time was near when we realized that the Polish community is preparing for some kind of activity.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Some people were talking about insurrection.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Some people were talking about the Resistance.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Some people were talking about mobilization.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I-- and then, all of a sudden, the rumors began to spread that the Russians are upon us in Warsaw, and that the Russian army is coming near Warsaw, and that they are disengaged from the agreement that Molotov and Ribbentrop had made in 1939.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they are at odds with themselves.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they are now enemies.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the Russians are coming upon the Germans.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we better-- the Polish people, the Polish military decided that they better try to get into the act and perhaps start some kind of a resistance and perhaps retake Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was in the summer of 1944, [PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] I believe.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
